154249722.description: The same great tartan flannel as in our men's shirt, designed just for you.  Relaxed Fit: Our most generous fit sits farthest from the body.  Falls at low hip.  Made of high-quality Portuguese cotton flannel, an L.L.Bean exclusive.  Expertly brushed for exceptional softness and warmth.  Authentic Scottish tartan patterns are specially yarn-dyed so they'll stay bright.  Machine wash and dry.  Button-front styling.  Chest pocket.  Shirttail hem.  Imported.
154249722.title: L.L.Bean Scotch Plaid Shirt, Relaxed

183214727.description: An instant update for your workwear wardrobe, these Max Mara slim leg trousers are fashioned with lambs leather side stripes for a sports luxe twist on tailoring. 183214727.title: Max Mara Slim Leg Trousers
